HEADWORD: Iron-gray
<hw>I"ron-gray`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Of a gray color,
somewhat resembling that of iron freshly broken.</def> --
<def2><pos>n.</pos> <def>An iron-gray color; also, a horse of this
color.</def></def2>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

